HEADWORD: Sale
<hw>Sale</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>See 1st
<er>Sallow</er>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
